<html>
<head>
<meta charset='UTF-8'>
[% INCLUDE new_tt2/top_css_js.tt2 %]
</head>
<body>
[% INCLUDE new_tt2/header.tt2 %]

<h3>
Greetings $rec_fname,
</h3>
<p>Your friend has sent you a gift card for meals and lodging at Mount Madonna Center.
It has a value of \$${amount}.</p>
<p>
It was sent to you by $first ${last}.</p>
<p>
You can redeem it (in whole or in part) by registering
for a Personal Retreat (or any other program) at <a target=_blank href='https://www.mountmadonna.org'>mountmadonna.org</a>.</p>
<p>
When paying for your registration use this gift card code: <span style="font-size: 15pt">$code</span>
[% IF personal_note %]
</p>
<p>
${first}'s message to you is this:</p>
<ul>
$personal_note_verbose
</ul>
[% END %]
<p>
You can check on the status of your card with <a href='$cgi/gift_card_status?code=$code'>this link</a>.<br>
<strong>Thank you</strong>
</p>

<!-- // PAGE CONTENT ENDS HERE -->
[% INCLUDE new_tt2/footer.tt2 %]
</body>
</html>
